    <!-- About Section -->
    <section id="about" class="about">
        <div class="section-content">
            <h2 class="section-title fade-in">About Me</h2>
            <div class="about-content fade-in">
                <p>As an undergraduate student at the Indian Institute of Science, I am pursuing a B.Tech in Mathematics and Computing with a strong academic record (CGPA: 8.1/10). My research interests span Deep Learning Architectures, Computer Vision, Natural Language Processing, and Mathematical Computing.</p>
                <p>I have demonstrated exceptional academic excellence, achieving International Rank 1 in the International Mathematics Olympiad and securing the 87th International Rank in the National Cyber Olympiad. My technical expertise includes advanced knowledge of deep learning frameworks, programming languages, and mathematical foundations.</p>
                <p>Beyond academics, I serve as the Founding Chairperson of the IISc ACM-W Student Chapter, where I lead initiatives to promote women in computing and organize technical workshops. I am also an active participant in the IISc Drama Club and a District Basketball Medalist.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Research Section -->
    <section id="research" class="research">
        <div class="section-content">
            <h2 class="section-title fade-in">Research & Projects</h2>
            <div class="research-grid">
                <div class="research-item fade-in">
                    <h3>Advanced Decoder-Only Language Model</h3>
                    <p>Developed a sophisticated transformer-based architecture for creative text generation, implementing custom loss functions and sampling strategies. The model achieved an impressive 85% human evaluation score for joke coherence and creativity, demonstrating its effectiveness in natural language generation tasks.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="research-item fade-in">
                    <h3>Geniebox: Intelligent Email Processing</h3>
                    <p>Created a scalable Firebase-based application capable of processing over 1000 emails daily. The system features advanced NLP algorithms for promotional code extraction with 92% accuracy and integrates real-time validation through RESTful APIs.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="research-item fade-in">
                    <h3>Advanced Variational Autoencoder</h3>
                    <p>Designed and implemented a novel VAE architecture with custom loss functions for image processing. The project achieved a 30% improvement in image quality metrics compared to baseline models through optimized KL divergence and enhanced latent space representation.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

